    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Root cause:** Off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts` — the `processItems` loop condition reads `i < items.length - 1`, which stops one step short, skipping the last element every time. For a single-element array, nothing runs at all.\n\n**The fix is a one-character change on line 7:**\n\n```typescript\n// Before (buggy)\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n\n// After (fixed)\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\n**Impact:** 3 of 4 tests in `tests/utils.test.ts` are currently failing. After removing the `- 1`, all 4 will pass.\n\nApprove the plan to proceed with the fix?",
